author: J. Edward Moreno
title: Protestors gather in front of Michigan governor's house to call on her to reopen the state
description: Protestors on Thursday gathered in front of Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer's (D) home in Lansing to call on her to reopen the state amid the coronavirus pandemic.
content:
Protestors on Thursday gathered in front of Michigan Gov. Gretchen Whitmer's (D) home in Lansing to call on her to reopen the state amid the coronavirus pandemic.
